ttp_template:
<group name="issuer_serial_number_status_subject">
  Status: {{STATUS | ORPHRASE}}
  cn: {{ISSUER | ORPHRASE}}
  Certificate Serial Number: {{SERIAL_NUMBER | ORPHRASE}}
  Certificate Usage: {{USAGE | ORPHRASE}}
  Name: {{SUBJECT | ORPHRASE}}
  start date: {{VALID_FROM | ORPHRASE}}
  end date: {{VALID_TO | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
Certificate
  Status: Available
  Certificate Serial Number: 0A1234B5678C
  Certificate Usage: General Purpose

    cn: Example CA
  Subject:
    Name: cn=Example Device
  Validity Date:
    start date: 01:00:00 UTC Jan 1 2023

textfsm_template:
Value STATUS (\S+)
Value SERIAL_NUMBER (\S+)
Value USAGE (.+)
Value ISSUER (.+)
Value SUBJECT (.+)
Value VALID_FROM (\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} UTC [a-zA-Z]{3} \d{1,2} \d{4})
Value VALID_TO (\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2} UTC [a-zA-Z]{3} \d{1,2} \d{4})

Start
  ^\s*Certificate\s*$$
  ^\s*Status:\s+${STATUS}\s*$$
  ^\s*Certificate\s+Serial\s+Number:\s+${SERIAL_NUMBER}\s*$$
  ^\s*Certificate\s+Usage:\s+${USAGE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Issuer:\s*$$
  ^\s*cn:\s+${ISSUER}\s*$$
  ^\s*Subject:\s*$$
  ^\s*Name:\s+${SUBJECT}\s*$$
  ^\s*Validity\s+Date:\s*$$
  ^\s*start\s+date:\s+${VALID_FROM}\s*$$
  ^\s*end\s+date:\s+${VALID_TO}\s*$$ -> Record
